data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom, 4 bath colonial in the desirable development, The Reserves of Willoughby.   The open concept main floor features a living room, family room with gas fireplace, large eat-in kitchen, and a morning room.  Off the morning room you walk out to a spacious stamped concrete patio with electric awning to provide shade on those sunny days.  The backyard is fully fenced in and includes a swim spa.  Upstairs you will find 3 large bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.  The owners suite features a large walk in closet and a full bath with soaking tub.  The upstairs also includes a loft, great for a home office.  Don't forget about the finished basement with half bath.  Don't miss out, schedule your home tour today!
